dct_title_s: Provincia Momomiae: The province of Mounster; Amstelodami, sumptibus Joannis Janssonij.; Provincia Momomiae: The province of Movnster;Province of Munster
dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Includes drawings of ships and a sea monster in the ocean. This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1636, 1637, and 1680. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map: 37 x 47 cm.
dct_rights_sm: This map is in the public domain.
